#summary Unresolved Turmites of 2 state and 2 colors.

= Introduction =

There are 531 unique unresolved 2-state 2-color turmites. This is a subpage of EdPeggsBusyBeaverTurmiteChallenge.

I simulated all 2<sup>16</sup>=65,536 rules of the 2s2c turmites and noted how much of each type resolved at regular iteration steps (powers of 10).

Unique rules exclude reflections, rotations, 'odd' rotations and slower versions.
